v0.1.0.description:
Initial release of the Pikmin apworld for Archipelago:
- All ship parts implemented as both locations and items
- Area unlocks controlled by collecting 1/5/12/29 ship parts through Archipelago, currently only in vanilla order
- Supports European version and North American revision 1

Setup instructions and more information here: https://github.com/Poke714/Archipelago/wiki
v0.1.0.title: Pikmin Archipelago 0.1.0
